==结构==
XeF<sub>6</sub>结构的确定颇费了一些时间。气态时的六氟化氙为单分子，采取略畸变的[[八面体|八面体]]结构，能迅速发生分子重排，存在着几种电子排列的[[异构体|异构体]]。进一步计算表明，该分子的点群为C<sub>3v</sub>，但计算结果也说明O<sub>h</sub>点群只是略高一些。<ref>{{cite journal|last = Seppelt|first = Konrad|date=June 1979|title = Recent Developments in the Chemistry of Some Electronegative Elements|journal = Accounts of Chemical Research|volume = 12|issue = 6|pages = 211–216|doi = 10.1021/ar50138a004}}</ref>稀有气体和氟化学权威Konrad Seppelt认为，对结构最好的描述是一对电子在八面体的面和角上移动，因此造成了动力学的变形。<ref>{{cite journal
 | last = Seppelt
 | first = Konrad
 | title = Recent Developments in the Chemistry of Some Electronegative Elements
 | journal = Accounts of Chemical Research
 | volume = 12
 | issue = 6
 | pages = 211–216
 | doi = 10.1021/ar50138a004
 |date=June 1979}}</ref>固态时，六氟化氙为四聚体，四个等同的氙处于[[四面体|四面体]]的[[頂點_(分子構型)|顶点]]，24个氟位于外围，可以发生相互交换。

六种{{chem|XeF|6}}的[[同质异形体|同质异形体]]是已知的，<ref name="Hoyer">{{Cite journal | first1 = S. |last1= Hoyer | first2 = K. | last2 = Emmler | first3 = T. | last3 = Seppelt| title = The structure of xenon hexafluoride in the solid state| journal = Journal of Fluorine Chemistry | volume = 127 | issue = 10| pages = 1415–1422| issn = 0022-1139 | doi = 10.1016/j.jfluchem.2006.04.014 | date = October 2006}}</ref> 其中一种还包含 XeF{{su|b=5|p=+}} 离子和桥接配体 F{{su|p=−}} 离子。<ref name="jehouse">{{cite book|title = Inorganic Chemistry|url = https://archive.org/details/inorganicchemist00jeho|url-access = limited|author = James E. House|publisher = Academic Press|year = 2008|isbn = 978-0-12-356786-4|page = [https://archive.org/details/inorganicchemist00jeho/page/n583 569]}}</ref>

==反应==
===水解反应===
六氟化氙分多步[[水解|水解]]，最终产物是[[三氧化氙|三氧化氙]]：<ref>{{cite journal | last = Appelman | first = E. H. | coauthors = and J. G. Malm | title = Hydrolysis of Xenon Hexafluoride and the Aqueous Solution Chemistry of Xenon | journal = Journal of the American Chemical Society | volume = 86 | issue = 11 | pages = 2141–2148 | doi = 10.1021/ja01065a009|date=June 1964}}</ref>
:XeF<sub>6</sub> + H<sub>2</sub>O  →  XeOF<sub>4</sub>  +  2 HF
:XeOF<sub>4</sub> + H<sub>2</sub>O  →  XeO<sub>2</sub>F<sub>2</sub>  +  2 HF
:XeO<sub>2</sub>F<sub>2</sub>  +  H<sub>2</sub>O  →  XeO<sub>3</sub>  +  2 HF

XeF<sub>6</sub>可作[[路易斯酸|路易斯酸]]与一个或两个氟离子反应生成[[配离子|配离子]]：
:XeF<sub>6</sub> + F<sup>−</sup> →  XeF<sub>7</sub><sup>−</sup>
:XeF<sub>7</sub><sup>−</sup> + F<sup>−</sup> → XeF<sub>8</sub><sup>2−</sup>

===八氟合氙(VI)酸盐===
六氟化氙与[[氟化铷|氟化铷]]生成的加合物[[铷|Rb]]<sub>2</sub>XeF<sub>8</sub>非常稳定，400°C以上才分解。<ref>Holleman, A. F.; Wiberg, E. "Inorganic Chemistry" Academic Press: San Diego, 2001. ISBN 0-12-352651-5.</ref>氙的另外两个常见氟化物，[[二氟化氙|二氟化氙]]和[[四氟化氙|四氟化氙]]不与氟离子生成稳定的路易斯酸碱[[加合物|加合物]]。

八氟合氙(VI)酸盐<span style="white-space: nowrap">(XeF{{su|b=8|p=2−}})</span>很稳定， 400 °C以上才分解。<ref name="holleman1" /><ref name="riedel1" /><ref name="chandra">{{cite book
| title = Comprehensive Inorganic Chemistry
| first1 = Sulekh
| last1 = Chandra
| publisher = New Age International
| year = 2004
| isbn = 81-224-1512-1
| page = 308
}}</ref> 这个阴离子的结构是[[四方反棱柱|四方反棱柱]]，是从它的[[亚硝酰|亚硝酰]]盐，[[八氟合氙(VI)酸亚硝酰|{{chem]]测量的。<ref name="peterson">{{Cite journal | first3 = A.| first2 = H. | first4 = M.| title = Antiprismatic Coordination about Xenon: the Structure of Nitrosonium Octafluoroxenate(VI)| first1 = W.| last2 = Holloway| last3 = Coyle| volume = 173| journal = Science| issue = 4003| pages = 1238–1239| issn = 0036-8075| doi = 10.1126/science.173.4003.1238| last4 = Williams| pmid = 17775218| last1 = Peterson| date = September 1971|bibcode = 1971Sci...173.1238P }}</ref> 它的钠盐和钾盐可以由[[氟化钠|氟化钠]]和[[氟化钾|氟化钾]]直接和六氟化氙化合而成：<ref name="chandra" />

:2 NaF + {{chem|XeF|6}} → {{chem|Na|2|XeF|8}}
:2 KF + {{chem|XeF|6}} → {{chem|K|2|XeF|8}}

它们的稳定性比对应的[[铯|铯]]盐和[[铷|铷]]盐低，而这些重碱金属氟化物和六氟化氙的反应是先形成七氟合氙(VI)酸盐：

:CsF + {{chem|XeF|6}}  →  {{chem|CsXeF|7}}
