===和氟离子接收剂的反应===

{{chem|XeF|6}} 会和强氟离子接收剂，如： {{chem|RuF|5}}<ref name="jehouse" /> 和 {{chem|BrF|3|·AuF|3}}<ref>{{cite book
| title = Advanced Inorganic Chemistry
| edition = 6th
| author = Cotton
| publisher = Wiley-India
| year = 2007
| isbn = 978-81-265-1338-3
| page = 591
}}</ref> 反应，形成 XeF{{su|b=5|p=+}} 阳离子：

:{{chem|XeF|6}} + {{chem|RuF|5}} → XeF{{su|b=5|p=+}}RuF{{su|b=6|p=−}}

:{{chem|XeF|6}} + {{chem|BrF|3|·AuF|3}} → XeF{{su|b=5|p=+}}AuF{{su|b=4|p=−}} + {{chem|BrF|3}}

